'''迈凯伦570S'''（{{lang-en|'''McLaren 570S'''}}）是[[迈凯伦汽车|迈凯伦汽车]]设计和制造的[[跑车|跑车]]，于2015年在[[纽约国际车展|纽约国际车展]]上揭幕。<ref>{{cite web|title=McLaren To Debut 570S Coupe At New York Auto Show|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/aliciaadamczyk/2015/03/29/mclaren-to-debut-570s-coupe-at-new-york-auto-show/|date=2015-03-29|first=Alicia|last=Adamczyk|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|accessdate=2015-03-30|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115161353/https://www.forbes.com/sites/aliciaadamczyk/2015/03/29/mclaren-to-debut-570s-coupe-at-new-york-auto-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The McLaren 570S is the Sports Series first car|url=http://www.roadandtrack.com/car-shows/new-york-auto-show/news/a25375/the-mclaren-570s-is-the-sports-series-first-car/|date=2015-03-25|first=Alex|last=Nunez|website=Road and Track|accessdate=2015-03-30|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126151249/https://www.roadandtrack.com/car-shows/new-york-auto-show/news/a25375/the-mclaren-570s-is-the-sports-series-first-car/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该款车型在英国定价为143,250英镑，<ref name="autocar.co.uk"/>而北美市场定价约为180,000美元。<ref name="autocar.co.uk"/>迈凯伦预计该款跑车可以帮助该公司在2020年前销售额翻两番，<ref>{{cite web|title=McLaren Unveils Its 570S Coupe, the Brand’s First Sports Car|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-03-30/mclaren-unveils-its-570s-coupe-the-brand-s-first-sports-car|date=2015-03-30|first=Hannah|last=Elliott|website=Bloomberg News|accessdate=2015-03-30|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202130045/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-03-30/mclaren-unveils-its-570s-coupe-the-brand-s-first-sports-car|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 设计 ==
该车拥有新一代代号为“M838T E”的3.8升双涡轮增压V8发动机，此引擎较前一代又大约百分之三十的部分得到了重新设计，之前已经在[[迈凯伦650S|迈凯伦650S]]和[[迈凯伦P1|迈凯伦P1]]上使用。该引擎为中置发动机配置，通过7速变速箱提供{{convert|562|bhp}}。该车自重{{convert|1313|kg}},[[功率重量比|功率重量比]]为每吨{{convert|428|bhp}}，燃油效率为{{convert|25.5|mpgimp}}，二氧化碳排放量为每公里258克。

迈凯伦汽车推出570S的目的，是在已有的强调运动性能的产品之外，提供一种拥有较大空间、更适合日常实用性的款式。<ref name="autocar.co.uk"/><ref name="motorauthority"/><ref>{{cite web|title=The McLaren 570S|url=http://cars.mclaren.com/featured-articles/the-mclaren-570s.html|website=mclaren.com|accessdate=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201040931/http://cars.mclaren.com/featured-articles/the-mclaren-570s.html|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 分支 ==
=== 540C ===
在2015年[[上海国际汽车工业博览会|上海国际车展]]上，迈凯伦还推出了540C作为其入门型号，该型号能提供{{convert|533|bhp}}。540C的售价比570S更低，约为126,000英镑。不过该型号不会再美国市场出现，因为迈凯伦公司希望在北美市场重点销售570S。

